{"tid":227360,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[踏上素食之路]牛要戒，菜就十月先要戒","createTime":"2017-05-03T06:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T17:03:47.000Z","uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0be67f8cc20af06f3be69d4d2f644d2da48ed505","tid":227360,"uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"好想慢慢食多啲素<br />\n由其係自己/兩三個朋友食飯嘅時候<br />\n香港有無啲素菜係值得推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊交流分享吓<br />\n咩國菜都得，傳統齋又得<br />\n<br />\n利申：深刻嘅得蘇波榮，野唔算好好食，但成個體驗係開心，亦都feel到誠意"},{"pid":"323883af4f8230f8bc3d1ba712338392047cdeb6","tid":227360,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"點解會有咁嘅諗頭？"},{"pid":"898e35890773d12f12ed26babfa02a60b4bc3681","tid":227360,"uid":34965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會有咁嘅諗頭？</blockquote><br />\n健康係其中一個考慮因素<br />\n但其實主要係自己鍾意食素菜<br />\n食完好多肉個人硬係唔自在咁<br />\n唔知心理定乜<br />\n反而有時煮麵烚菜食豆腐個人好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8937e6157b154a74719414cccb49200af56c9ca1","tid":227360,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b045ce8e914927deedbe691a1abfeb9a30f904bd","tid":227360,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"大多數素食店d野都落勁多油，有d仲炸過"},{"pid":"2372ae8bd87e034f9af4bf1abd86e725962cf7d4","tid":227360,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"太古銀杏時光幾好食<br />\n雖然我只係食過一次可能唔係好有參考價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但食完會有想再食多次嘅念頭<br />\n佢有肉但係都有素嘅餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c20c6749a47eddc5c921b9dc9895988b87e7f45","tid":227360,"uid":86151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"我最近都盡量一個人出街食飯嘅時間食素，不過通常一星期得兩三餐"},{"pid":"ae4fc847560daea1e0f2e6c563a312052147a597","tid":227360,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"好少食肉 純粹唔鍾意食<br />\n<br />\n利申老豆以前開肉檔<br />\n食厭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家煮肉出來都係一舊試完味就算<br />\n青椒肉絲 食晒辣椒 肉就倒左佢"},{"pid":"8bea4de0df7aeefa8a1a094f29560a64039335cf","tid":227360,"uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太古銀杏時光幾好食<br />\n雖然我只係食過一次可能唔係好有參考價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但食完會有想再食多次嘅念頭<br />\n佢有肉但係都有素嘅餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀杏都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但唔算平"},{"pid":"b009176f00d125060e4f2d1f94fdc9be0d969c03","tid":227360,"uid":91747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:16:21.000Z","msg":"薄大一念素食都好食"},{"pid":"d9294bb78a7f726eb5533d001a0986a6df3acb7f","tid":227360,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"元朗素苗有冇試過，正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab4f3b94ecc533f47afbe3fd65cb941a03e9fba","tid":227360,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薄大一念素食都好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講唔記得 一講起又想食<br />\n一念嘅春卷腐皮卷係世界級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dbaf6dd4584b5dae401411c38f47d7ec4fd09f","tid":227360,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"佐敦普光齋下午茶"},{"pid":"b56db26816bc996b4fa2beab4bf037cb5879ae5a","tid":227360,"uid":113020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"抵食既有:<br 